# Force LF line endings in the repo for all text files. Without this,
# Windows clients with `core.autocrlf=true` commit CRLF, and Prettier's
# format:check leg fails on Windows runners after git converts LF→CRLF
# on checkout. Pinning to LF makes format checks consistent across OSes.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binaries that must NEVER be normalised
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tgz binary
